description: Try our easy to follow Asian-Style Skewers recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Asian-Style Skewers Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 0.25 cup coriander, chopped leaves and root

recipeInstructions.text: Place coriander leaves, root, spring onion, oils and spice sachet in a food processor and process until a smooth paste forms.
Lay skewers on a baking paper-lined tray and brush all over with paste. Set aside for 15 minutes.
Heat on BBQ plate on medium-high. Cook skewers for 10 minutes, turning frequently until golden and cooked through. Serve with green salad.
